'''Su Des''' was a [[Cloning/Legends|cloning]] station on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]]. It was located in the northern hemisphere of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. An additional two million clones for a second generation were processed here and at [[Baran Wu]].

